<Layout title="The Three Tests for Predictive Intelligence | PresciaIQ Insights — Foundation Series Issue 03" description="How to tell real predictive AI tools from dashboards in costume. Three tests every Australian business should apply before buying any predictive software.">
  <article class="pt-28 pb-20 px-4 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
